Octociz had cease fi on the mercenairies. Many more had joined the 
fight, and he was no longer needed. He looked for a place to go, and 
zoomed his optics a bit father from the battle. Prowl and Iron Raptor 
were basically scrap. Iron Raptor is trying to get Prowl to a CR 
Chamber, but she won't make it. She needs one herself. Octociz runs 
over to them to see if they need any help.
